      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>Indole reacts with electrophiles at C3 rather than at C2. Draw resonance forms of the intermediate cations resulting from reaction at C2 and C3, and explain the observed results.</p>\n",
